.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-CHECK-CONFIG" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-check-config \- show key node configuration settings
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-check-config
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns selected important settings from
.BR listconfigs ,
including network, fee policy, and HTLC limits.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"config_count":N, "key_settings":{...}}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-info (1),
.BR lightning-node-fee-policy (1)
